# UI Components Guide

## Component Organization

- **Ui Components**: Reusable UI elements in [src/components/Ui/](mdc:src/components/Ui/)
- **Project Components**: Project-specific components in [src/components/Project/](mdc:src/components/Project/)
- **Header Components**: Navigation components in [src/components/Header/](mdc:src/components/Header/)

## Key UI Components

- [Button.astro](mdc:src/components/Ui/Button.astro): Reusable button component
- [Card.astro](mdc:src/components/Ui/Card.astro): Card layout component
- [Glow.astro](mdc:src/components/Ui/Glow.astro): Glow effect component
- [Section.astro](mdc:src/components/Ui/Section.astro): Section wrapper component

## Styling Patterns

- Use Tailwind CSS classes consistently
- Component-specific styles in [src/styles/components/](mdc:src/styles/components/)
- Follow existing design patterns for consistency

## Component Props

- Use TypeScript interfaces for component props
- Keep components focused and single-purpose
- Follow the existing prop patterns in the codebase
